{"search_data": "HaryanaHaryana Mukhyamantri Vyapari Kshatipurti Bima Yojana (Insurance Scheme for Traders) Haryana govt. starts Mukhyamantri Vyapari Kshatipurti Beema Yojana to provide insurance coverage to traders, retailers, shopkeepers & self employed persons, insurance ranges from Rs. 5 lakh to Rs. 25 lakh on basis of their turnover, Mukhyamantri Vyapari Samuhik Niji Durghatna Beema Yojana 2019 also launched to provide Rs. 5 lakh insurance \u0939\u093f\u0902\u0926\u0940 \u092e\u0947\u0902 \u092a\u0922\u093c\u0947\u0902Haryana Mukhyamantri Vyapari Kshatipurti Bima YojanaThe important features and highlights of this scheme are as follows:-Haryana CM Vyapari Kshatipurti Bima YojnaLaunch Date11 September 2019Who are its BeneficiariesAll registered small and medium traders, retailers, shopkeepers & self employed personsNumber of Beneficiaries3.13 lakhCases for ApplicabilityGovt. will compensate loss of trader\u2019s stock caused due to fire, theft, flood and earthquake and damage to furniture and other goodsAmount of InsuranceRs. 5 Lakh to Rs. 25 LakhTurnover LimitRs. 5 lakh insurance for annual turnover upto Rs. 20 lakh, Rs. 10 lakh insurance coverage for turnover b/w Rs. 20 lakh to Rs. 50 lakh, Rs. 15 lakh insurance cover for turnover b/w Rs. 50 lakh to Rs. 1 crore, Insurance cover of Rs. 20 lakh for turnover b/w Rs. 1 crore to Rs. 1.5 crore, Rs. 25 lakh for traders having turnover of more than Rs. 1.5 crore.An insurance cover of Rs. 5 lakh to Rs. 25 lakh would be provided to registered traders on the basis of their turnover.The loss of stock due to any of the above mentioned reasons would attract compensation from the Haryana govt. Around 3.13 lakh registered small and medium traders would be benefited under this scheme.\u092e\u0941\u0916\u094d\u092f\u092e\u0902\u0924\u094d\u0930\u0940 \u0928\u0947 \u0935\u094d\u092f\u093e\u092a\u093e\u0930\u093f\u092f\u094b\u0902 \u0915\u0947 \u0932\u093f\u090f '\u092e\u0941\u0916\u094d\u092f\u092e\u0902\u0924\u094d\u0930\u0940 